abstract: The former Facebook executive, Owen Van Natta, now heads Project Playlist, a social music site the labels accuse of piracy.
snippet: The former Facebook executive, Owen Van Natta, now heads Project Playlist, a social music site the labels accuse of piracy.
lead_paragraph: What does Owen Van Natta know about how to make money from music on the Internet that hundreds of others before him couldn’t figure out?

headline.main: How Will Owen Van Natta Turn Piracy Into Profits?
